reviewText: I have been looking for this collection of Dennis the Menace for the longest time so that I could share it with my grandchildren, especially my six-year-old grandson, who so reminds me of him that he is has always been my real life "Dennis the Menace!"
I used to watch the Dennis the Menace TV series when I was a kid so I thought that my grand children would like it too---they do !!!!
for kids. It's okay
We grew up watching Dennis The Menace and my kids love love love the collection.

Watched "Dennis The Menace" again after a long time. Hilarious and very natural action from Dennis, Mr. Wilson and others like the robber. Though, not Blu-ray, the DVD quality is very good (full-screen on 50+ inch LCD TV). Haven't got a chance to watch the other two movies in the set. The price is very good for 3 movies in a set.

These are three family-friendly hilarous comedies that everyone can enjoy. Dennis the Menace has been popular for generations, and now we can share this set with all the kids -- young and old. Nothing objectionable here, just some silly, crazy fun. Love every one! Great price!
My grandson, who is very energetic, loves the "Dennis the Menace" movies.  He will sit and watch them over and over!!
There is a couple swear words. This was the only thing I didn't like. I had to talk to my kids about not repeating them.
My son loves Dennis!!!!! He watch it over and over again! He sleep with it and take everywhere he goes! All of them. Thank you for Dennis!

I bought these DVD's for my grandchildren and can't wait to watch 'Dennis' with them. I think they are fun movies for all ages. I hope I don't get blamed for any 'bad habits' they pick up from 'Dennis'!
Good movies ,Great Collection Pack but like others reviews, the first is the better of all!
